---
description: Agent Memory workspace-local context rules
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Agent Memory when recording project context.

- Keep facts, assumptions, evidence, and follow-up separate.
- Do not store credentials, tokens, private prompts, or personal data.
- Prefer run-scoped notes under `.opendock/` for temporary analysis.
- Run `node .opendock/harness/opendock__agent-memory/check.mjs` before handoff when possible.
